╭───────────────────────── Agent Keybindings ──────────────────────────╮
│                                                                      │
│ GLOBAL                                                               │
│  Ctrl-e         │ Close panel                                        │
│  Ctrl-w h/l     │ Focus diff / agent                                 │
│  Ctrl-w o       │ Toggle fullscreen                                  │
│                                                                      │
│ INSERT MODE                                                          │
│  Enter          │ Send prompt                                        │
│  Ctrl-j         │ Insert newline                                     │
│  Esc            │ Exit to normal                                     │
│  /              │ Slash commands                                     │
│  @              │ File picker                                        │
│                                                                      │
│ NORMAL MODE                                                          │
│  i/a/I/A        │ Enter insert                                       │
│  Space s        │ Toggle diff view                                   │
│  Space t        │ Cycle model variant                                │
│  ?              │ This help                                          │
│                                                                      │
│                                                                      │
╰───────────────────────── ? or Esc to close ──────────────────────────╯
